    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This kit consists of a heavy wooden box or leather pouch belt stuffed with the tools of the mechanik’s trade. In addition to common mechanik’s tools such as wrenches, hammers, and bolt drivers, a mechanik’s toolkit includes an array of other instruments, including several varieties of ratchets, pliers, tongs, spanners, calipers, and dividers. The kit of a mechanik who works on steamjacks will also include bores, chisels, reamers, scrapers, injectors for priming pneumatic chambers, expanders for piston cylinders, and several more esoteric items besides. Proficiency with a mechanik’s toolkit lets you add your proficiency bonus to any ability checks you make to craft or repair mechanika, steamjacks, and similar devices.</p>",
